Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to disgrace yourself by crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anything but my afro! Anything but my afro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you beg me to spare your life,\Njust like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not how it will go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While waiting for my chance to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have spent these past five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...growing stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Man's Promise Never Dies!!\NTo the Friend Waiting Under the Distant Sky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster that could tower over giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He's the one who made\Nall that noise and screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Luffy's zombie is hooting\Nand hollering as he runs rampant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! There's Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That skeleton knew\Nwhat he was talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Those stairs led to the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell through all\Nthat fog when we barged in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the stairway up was a shortcut\Nto the last boss's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Folding stairs...? Is this how\Nwe're supposed to get down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Man, we've been wiped clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zombies must have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are muddy footprints everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They could still be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they looted us, all right.\NNot that we have anything worth taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any zombies...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the guys in question?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that their zombies will also die
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if Luffy and the guys are exposed to sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. Chopper and Franky,\Nyou two search the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin and I will search the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies could still be hiding\Nsomewhere on board, so be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found them! Hey, I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the dining room!\NAll three of them are up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... could they do such a thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zombies had a blast "decorating" them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Luffy! Man, you can't\Nsleep looking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up! This isn't\Nthe time to catch some Z's!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a serious problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they even have a nervous system?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're askin' for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, outta the way. I'm using my bazooka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hot master swordswoman with meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"Hot"?\N--"Meat"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"Master swordswoman"?!\N--These guys are hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Didn't he say 95-55-85?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...miraculous measurements!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. You'll look lovely in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's get you changed right quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, geezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now! I'm doing it for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you leered at the naked flesh of\Nthe woman about to wed Absalom-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would make you pay dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Absalom-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was... still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in rottin' trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He noticed I was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Have the General Zombies congregate\Nin the ceremony hall! Hop to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give my shadow--\N--Calm down! Moria isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny?! What are we doing back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... None of that was a dream...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shadow is missing! This feels so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is bad! We have a disaster\Non hand! We're all out of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our galley packed nicely,\Nbut now it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took off with everything\Nbut some emergency rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live off cheese and\Ndried bread! Gimme meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really humiliating. I wasn't\Ntaking things seriously enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my pirate lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese doesn't cut it! Cheese bites!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I don't see Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let her get abducted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you follow her\Nto the ends of the earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! But it's not like\NI could just run after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is the jerk?!\NI'll get her back before you can bat an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait! Please hear me out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generally speaking, there are\Ntwo things we need to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our food, Nami, and our shadows, right?\NThat's three things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I wasn't expecting you\Nto rank things in that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, let me fill you in\Nabout Nami and your shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--? M-M-Marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got guts to marry Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is a giant version of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you make a zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've already found Luffy's\Nand the cook's zombies, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I had no idea he was one\Nof the Seven Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear suddenly set in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were we supposed to know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If the zombies act just like us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I saw your zombie, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No different from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scars on the back are a swordsman's shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am covered in scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he wasn't you,\Nsince he was wearing sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to find a zombie in sandals,\NLuffy's giant, and the cook's dogguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our shadows will come back if we\Nthrow salt in their mouths, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly, I'm amazed you\Ndiscovered that weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our info came from that bag of bones,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from how to defeat the zombies\Nto how to rescue you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! You saw Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did. And I asked him a\Nstupid question when I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I totally rejected his very\Nexistence when you first brought him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aboard our ship to join our crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a flimsy skeleton,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I talked to him,\Nhe had an iron backbone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One fitting for a skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to ask him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll have to pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of everything you've told us,\Nanswer this one question before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how people will react
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you appear before them\Nas you are now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a talking skeleton!\NYou'll never make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The abnormal are ostracized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you leave the Devil's Sea,\Nyour fate is sealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to make matters worse, you've spent\Nthe past several decades trapped here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say, "I got so\Nlonely that I wanted to die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I would have\Ntaken my own life ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence bites...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you act like a gentleman\Nto hide the core of the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing all of this because\Nyou want to keep a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did you promise your crewmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather nosy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:18:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, we left a member of my\Ncrew behind at a certain location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was unavoidable, yet sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we set sail, we vehemently\Nswore that we would return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then we were annihilated on these seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,preventing us from keeping our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the sole survivor from our ship,\Nit is my duty to tell him what has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it has been... fifty years\Nnow since the day we died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years?! Hey, that was ages ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't even born yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I doubt he's been waiting that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What right...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What right do I have to decide\Nwhether or not he's still waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's still waiting for us,\Nbelieving that we'll keep our promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine how lonesome he must feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's still waiting while under\Nthe belief that we've betrayed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can you imagine how miserable he must be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We swore to reunite with my crewmate\Noff some capes. His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a young whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we couldn't possibly bring him\Nwith us on our dangerous voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whale...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine he's grown rather big by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your crewmate... is a whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I can't help but\Nthink he still believes in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he thinks we'll play\Nour typical lively music
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and come back waving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he will forgive us for\Nirresponsibly dying on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a selfish promise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and died under a distant sky where\Nour voices couldn't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry we died" could never cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave our word as men that we would return!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why he's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Chopper wasn't there for this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...! What the hell did\Nyou do to my special seat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm strong, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fight isn't over yet!\NSo we have to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your buddies're dead,\Nbut I'm your rival forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely have to fight again\Nin order to decide who is stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After going around the Grand Line,\Nwe'll come back to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I come back, let's fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm. This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the symbol of our promise to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we come back, don't remove\Nthat mark by hitting your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cape on the Grand Line...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait! He's still waiting after fifty years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a touching story!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that skeleton\Nto have a past like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Swear to Go See Him!!\NBrook and the Cape of Promise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
